      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "NT"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      w-cnt-acc-sav-l23    to   v-nt1                  .
           move      w-cnt-acc-sav-l24    to   v-nt2                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       exe-acc-cmp-exi-920.
