      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-des-stp (1)    to   w-all-str-alf          .
           move      40                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           perform   all-str-upp-000      thru all-str-upp-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-tes-des-key (1)      .
       acc-des-stp-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
